title: Grateful Dead Live at Hampton Coliseum on 1986-03-20
lineage: MC > Playback on Marantz PRD505 (azimuth adjusted) > Marantz Intergrated Stereo Amp MP-68 > SB Audigy4 on new P4 machine > Sound Forge normalization > WAV > CDWave > WAVs > Flacfrontend 1.7.1 (level 8) > flacs

Set 1

reviews.review_text: 1st Box of Rain in years Was at this show. First Box in years. The crowd is going crazy throughout most of the song. One of the many fond memories of Dead shows that I have.
